      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a car back to life! While it currently needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it serves as a great foundation for a restoration or a valuable source of parts. Grab this budget-friendly diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
